high_descs: Turn to the left, walk to the end of the red chair, then turn left, walk a few steps, then turn left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the credit card that is on the kitchen table.
Turn around completely, walk to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the floor lamp.
Turn off the floor lamp that is in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Turn off the floor lamp while holding a credit card.

high_descs: Turn left and walk past the red couch then turn left and walk to the chair on the side of the dining room table then turn left to face it.
Pick up the credit card that's in front of you near the laptop on the table.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the light.
Look up and turn off the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn off a light as you hold a credit card.

high_descs: Turn to make a left and then another left to reach the table.
Pick up the red credit card on the table.
Turn to make a right towards the tall lamp next to the couch.
anns.task_desc: Look at a red credit card under a lit tall lamp.
